Package: psycCleaning
Type: Package
Title: Toolkit for Data Cleaning
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jason Moy
Maintainer: Jason Moy <jmoy1@uw.edu>
Description: A beginner-friendly R package that contains many useful functions for data cleaning for psychological research, such as composite test scores, re-coding items, and summarizing number of NA values in a data frame. 
